		"_postman_id": "kks-products-api-collection",
		"name": "KKS Online - Products API",
		"description": "Postman collection for testing KKS Online Backend Product APIs\n\n**Base URL**: `http://localhost:3000`\n\n**API Version**: v1\n\nThis collection includes:\n- V1 API endpoints (recommended)\n- Legacy endpoints (for backwards compatibility)\n- Product variations endpoints\n\n**Setup Instructions**:\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Create an environment variable `base_url` with value `http://localhost:3000`\n3. Ensure the Rust backend is running on port 3000\n4. Start testing!",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
